Accounts example code

Bitcointalk

2010-12-10 19:21:03 UTC - [11]Original Post

   Some sample pseudocode using the new Accounts based commands in 0.3.18.
   print "send to " + getaccountaddress(username) + " to fund your
   account"
   print "balance: " + getbalance(username, 0)
   print "available balance: " + getbalance(username, 6)
   // if you make a sale, move the money from their account to your ""
   account
   if (move(username, "", amount, 6, "purchased item"))
       SendTheGoods()
   // withdrawal
   sendfrom(username, bitcoinaddress, amount, 6, "withdrawal by user")
   You can use listtransactions(username) to show them a list of their
   recent transactions.
